{"id":685154,"date":"2024-04-28T12:44:16","date_gmt":"2024-04-28T07:14:16","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/?p=685154"},"modified":"2025-09-04T16:51:08","modified_gmt":"2025-09-04T11:21:08","slug":"top-jobs-for-mca-freshers","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/top-jobs-for-mca-freshers","title":{"rendered":"Top jobs for MCA freshers"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Master of Computer Applications, or MCA, is a study domain that has picked up demand over the last few years, thanks to the rapid IT evolution. Information Technology is ever-evolving, bringing newer technologies to the table. MCA courses equip students with the desired skills and knowledge sets, enabling them to keep up with the times and significantly contribute to their career growth.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>This explains why there is always a need for MCA graduates in India. A <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cmr.edu.in\/blog\/the-benefits-of-a-career-in-mca-in-2023\/#:~:text=High%20Demand%20for%20MCA%20Graduates,IT%20professionals%2C%20including%20MCA%20graduates.\">recent NASSCOM report<\/a> anticipates a growth of 7.7% in the IT industry in India between the period ranging from 2021 to 2025.&nbsp; This blog looks at some of the top entry-level MCA jobs in the country that you can consider upon graduation in the domain.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-entry-level-mca-jobs\"><strong>Entry-level MCA jobs<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>As stated earlier, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/online-mca-an-affordable-path-to-a-tech-career\">MCA<\/a> lays down a lucrative career path with plenty of opportunities for freshers and experienced professionals alike. Listed below are some of the top job opportunities for MCA freshers:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><tbody><tr><td><strong>Expected job role<\/strong><\/td><td><strong>Job description<\/strong><\/td><td><strong>Avg annual salary (approx)<\/strong><\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Web Designer<\/td><td>Design a website\u2019s layout, provide code for web pages, and run tests to check website features<\/td><td><a href=\"https:\/\/6figr.com\/in\/salary\/web-design--s\">INR 20.9 lakhs per annum<\/a><\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Data Scientist<\/td><td>Analyze huge data sets and identify solutions to problems in a business organization<\/td><td><a href=\"https:\/\/www.payscale.com\/research\/IN\/Job=Data_Scientist\/Salary\">INR 971,043 per annum<\/a><\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Systems Analyst<\/td><td>Maintain IT systems, execute new systems, and monitor their effectiveness<\/td><td><a href=\"https:\/\/in.indeed.com\/career\/systems-analyst\/salaries\">INR 9,54,094 per annum<\/a><\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Database Administrator<\/td><td>Manage &amp; maintain databases of companies<\/td><td><a href=\"https:\/\/www.glassdoor.co.in\/Salaries\/database-administrator-salary-SRCH_KO0,22.htm\">INR 8,13,914 per annum<\/a><\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Software Developer<\/td><td>Design, execute, and manage software programs &amp; apps<\/td><td><a href=\"https:\/\/www.glassdoor.co.in\/Salaries\/software-developer-salary-SRCH_KO0,18.htm#:~:text=The%20average%20salary%20for%20Software%20Developer%20is%20%E2%82%B97%2C60%2C000,%E2%82%B960%2C000%2C%20with%20a%20range%20from%20%E2%82%B925%2C000%20-%20%E2%82%B91%2C50%2C000.\">INR 7,60,000 per annum<\/a><\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Software Engineer<\/td><td>Design, develop, and maintain computer software<\/td><td><a href=\"https:\/\/in.indeed.com\/career\/software-engineer\/salaries\">INR 7,20,521 per annum<\/a><\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Hardware Engineer<\/td><td>Develop, maintain, and test computers &amp; their physical parts<\/td><td><a href=\"https:\/\/www.payscale.com\/research\/IN\/Job=Hardware_Engineer\/Salary\">INR 5,50,393 per annum<\/a><\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Troubleshooter&nbsp;<\/td><td>Determine, analyze, and provide solutions for issues in computer hardware, software, or apps&nbsp;<\/td><td><a href=\"https:\/\/www.payscale.com\/research\/IN\/Skill=Troubleshooting\/Salary\">INR 4,23,000 per annum<\/a><\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-mca-career-path\"><strong>MCA career path<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Students and other <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/top-job-opportunities-in-tech\">tech professionals<\/a> opting for an MCA degree at the postgraduate level are highly likely to witness augmented growth in their careers. An MCA has the potential to instantly boost the chances of securing a high-paying job in the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/top-industries-for-mca-graduates\">IT industry<\/a>, in addition to a prestigious job title as well. MCA courses are also particularly helpful in imparting and enhancing the necessary technical skills that professionals in the tech industry require for growth in the IT sector.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-skills-required-for-mca-freshers\"><strong>Skills required for MCA freshers<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Students graduating with an MCA degree and applying for fresher jobs after MCA are generally expected to possess the following <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/enhance-your-technical-expertise-with-online-mca\">essential skills<\/a> by companies:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Knowledge of Database Management Systems such as Oracle and SQL<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Software architecture and design<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Critical thinking and problem-solving<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Time management skills<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Agile methodologies like Kanban and Scrum<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-companies-hiring-mca-graduates\"><strong>Companies hiring MCA graduates<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Now that we are well aware of the skills required to apply for <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/10-best-career-options-after-mca\"><strong>MCA graduate career options<\/strong><\/a><strong>, <\/strong>let us look at the top companies that are likely to hire these professionals after completion of their course:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Capgemini<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Wipro Technologies<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>HCL<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>IBM Global Services<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Accenture<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Computer Sciences Corporation<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Hewlett-Packard<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Cognizant Technology Solutions<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Tata Consultancy Services<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Tech Mahindra&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-conclusion\">Conclusion<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>An <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/online-mca-degree-muj\">online MCA degree<\/a> can be particularly helpful for finding rewarding career prospects after graduation. The blog above highlighted a few top opportunities for MCA fresher employment and there are many more to explore, considering the steadily increasing demand for the course in the IT sector.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sikkim Manipal University (SMU) offers <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/master-of-computer-applications-smu\">online MCA<\/a> courses to students in fully online mode on the Online Manipal University platform. The program is designed to equip students with the desired skills to take up diverse roles in varied industries.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Master of Computer Applications, or MCA, is a study domain that has picked up demand over the last few years, thanks to the rapid IT evolution. Information Technology is ever-evolving, bringing newer technologies to the table. MCA courses equip students with the desired skills and knowledge sets, enabling them to keep up with the times [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":19,"featured_media":677032,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[607],"tag